</HEADER>
<BODY>
<SLUG> BC-ELIMINATE-DOCTORS-REVOLT-NYT </SLUG>
  
<TEXT>
<P>
   EDITORS:
</P>
<P>
   DOCTORS-REVOLT (Washington) will not move in tonight's New York
Times News Service file.
</P>
<P>
   N.Y.Times News Service, Oct. 18.
</P>
