</P>
<P>
   Colorado St. 47, New Mexico St. 28
</P>
<P>
   E. Washington 44, Idaho St. 13
</P>
<P>
   Fairfield 24, San Diego 7
</P>
<P>
   Idaho 26, Utah St. 14
</P>
<P>
   Montana 33, N. Arizona 20
</P>
<P>
   Portland St. 34, Montana St. 31
</P>
<P>
   S. Utah 37, Fort Lewis 6
</P>
<P>
   Sacramento St. 35, CS Northridge 21
</P>
<P>
