<TEXT>
<P>
   EDITORS:
</P>
<P>
   MIDEAST-SUMMIT (Wye Mills, Md.) will not move in tonight's New
York Times News Service file.
</P>
<P>
   N.Y.Times News Service, Oct. 18.
</P>
</TEXT>
